{"type":null,"faqId":9476,"title":"P6S-U06  后台播放与退出音乐，歌词同步","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\"><span><span>l</span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">后台播放：进入</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">“</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">音乐</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">播放器</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">播放任意音频文件</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">播放过程中按</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">Back</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">或</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">Home</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">键。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\"><span><span>l</span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">退出音乐：在音乐播放界面，点击手机</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">Menu</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">键，选择退出，在弹出的框上选择确定，即可退出</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">音乐</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">应用。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\"><span><span>l</span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">歌词同步：当歌曲和对应的歌词存储在手机同一目录时，用户播放这首歌曲，歌词会自动加载。在播放界面，点击播放进度条上方的小三角按钮，可以打开歌词界面。在歌词界面，点击歌词，在界面会有两个按钮</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">延迟</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">秒</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">快进</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">秒</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，分别会将歌词延迟</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">秒和快进</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">秒。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"77","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396253425000,"seriesProductName":"P6 S-U00","visitedTimes":5,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}